   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Moros and his associate collectors of the crown tax for the viggage of Theogenis to Herakleides. We have received from you for the crown tax for Epeiph of year 4 eight drachmae, total 8 dr., and for the account of Choiak four drachmae, total 4 dr.</ab>
         </div>
